{
  "8again": {
    "format": "rules-card",
    "title": "8-Again",
    "subtitle": "Roll Quality",
    "blocks": [
      "Reroll dice that show 8, 9 or 10 (i.e. all successful dice). Keep rerolling until you get a failing result, accumulating successes as you go.",
      "If you gain 8-again on a roll that already had that quality, it may become a <strong>rote action</strong> at the Storyteller's discretion."
    ],
    "source": {
      "book": "DtR",
      "page": 189
    }
  },
  "9again": {
    "format": "rules-card",
    "title": "9-Again",
    "subtitle": "Roll Quality",
    "blocks": [
      "Reroll dice that show 9 or 10, as opposed to just 10. Keep rerolling until you get a result that isn't a 9 or 10, accumulating successes as you go.",
      "If you gain 9-again on a roll that already had that quality, it becomes <strong>8-again</strong> instead."
    ],
    "source": {
      "book": "DtR",
      "page": 188
    }
  },
  "meditation": {
    "format": "rules-card",
    "title": "Meditation",
    "subtitle": "Extended Action",
    "blocks": [
      "Meditation is an <strong>extended action</strong>.",
      "<span class='tooltip-list-item'><strong>Dice Pool:</strong> {{NAMEVALUE:com}} + {{NAMEVALUE:wit}}</span>",
      "<span class='tooltip-list-item'><strong>Target Successes:</strong> 4</span>",
      "<span class='tooltip-list-item'><strong>Interval:</strong> 30 minutes</span>",
      "After successfully meditating, {{NAME}} gains a +1 bonus to {{his}} next breaking point roll.",
      "Once this bonus is used or {{NAME}} sleeps, the benefits of meditation end and must be regained by meditating again.",
      "Soothing music or relaxation tapes can provide a <strong>+1</strong> to <strong>+2</strong> equipment bonus. A dedicated meditation room provides <strong>+3</strong>. Loud noises, an uncomfortable environment, or lack of sleep inflict a <strong>&minus;1</strong> penalty each. Lack of food inflicts a <strong>&minus;1</strong> to <strong>&minus;3</strong> penalty."
    ],
    "source": {
      "book": "CoD",
      "page": 75
    }
  },
