    "format": "rules-card",
    "title": "Rote Actions",
    "subtitle": "Roll Quality",
    "blocks": [
      "Reroll any dice that do not show an 8, 9, or 10, unless you're reduced to a chance die on a rote action and roll a dramatic failure.",
      "You may only reroll each die once."
    ],
